OL,5, More than 64,000 staff at Lloyds Bank  
OL,6, are to receive a #1,000 one-off payment
OL,7, to help with the rising cost of living 
OL,8, in the UK.                             
OL,10,FThe payment - due to be made in August 
OL,11,F- comes after a campaign by the union  
OL,12,FUnite, which demonstrated at Lloyds'   
OL,13,Fannual general meeting last month.     
OL,15,FUnite said it was a "important step" in
OL,16,Fchanging the bank's pay structures.    
OL,18,FIn a memo seen by the BBC, Lloyds said 
OL,19,Fthe money would help during uncertain  
OL,20,Feconomic times.                        
